# Doodlash Socket Events

- Event names and payloads must match `Doodlash_SDD.md` §5.3 (lobby) and §10 (game).
- Do not rename events (e.g. `join_lobby` → `joinRoom`) without updating the SDD.
- Adding a new event requires an SDD update first.
- Lobby ack events: `join_lobby`, `rejoin_lobby`.
- Game-critical events stay server-validated: `player_guess`, `draw_stroke`, `start_game`, `round_end`.
